selected_groups:
Each group ultimately selected by the algorithm is a tuple.

group_count:
The number of selected groups, which is len(selected_groups).

is_valid:
Is 100% coverage completed.
True：All targets are covered
False：Still have tagerts not being covered

runtime_ms:
run time(ms)

target_count:
How many target j-groups have been generated in total.

candidate_count_used:
The number of candidates actually participating in the search.

candidate_count_total:
The theoretical total number of k-groups.

mode
mode using now:
full-candidate：All candidate joined
heuristic：Too much candidate，adopted the heuristic candidate pool
